listitem.extension:
u^T_k u_{k'}^* 
 = \sum_{n=0}^{N-1} \left(e^{ \frac{2\pi i}{N} kn}\right) \left(e^{\frac{2\pi i}{N} (-k')n}\right)
 = \sum_{n=0}^{N-1} e^{ \frac{2\pi i}{N} (k-k') n} 
 = N~\delta_{kk'}

tablecell.extension:
\left\{ \begin{matrix}
 N & \mbox{if } a = e^{i 2 \pi k/N} \\
 \frac{1-a^N}{1-a \, e^{-i 2 \pi k/N} } & \mbox{otherwise}
 \end{matrix} \right.
